INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2251,2,'2013-04-21 19:21:42','2013-04-21 23:21:42','[caption id=\"attachment_174\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"216\"]<a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/http:/www.westcoast-east.com/page/sample-page.html/two-of-the-leather-bags-we-make/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-174\"><img class=\" wp-image-174  \" alt=\"Two of the leather bags we make – deerskin and leather.\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-2-bags-300x199.png\" width=\"216\" height=\"143\" /></a> The Algonquin and Sequoia handbags.[/caption]\n<h2>Our Product Selection</h2>\nThese relaxed yet sophisticated handbags offer style and everyday functionality. They are the perfect-size to handle the essentials, such as a phone, small wallet, comb, glasses and lipstick.\n\nThe size of the bag is perfect for a quick shopping trip. For a longer day, it\'s small and flexible and will easily fit in your briefcase or tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\n\nAll bags are carefully handcrafted and fully lined. They measure approximately 8 inches high and 5-1/2 inches across and weigh only a few ounces. Purse feet and a reinforced bottom allow bag to stand upright. Drawstring closure doubles as a wrist strap.\n\nEach style offers something a little different; The Algonquin is a stylish leather bag, the Tahoe is a totally vegan bag, and the Niagara is the perfect bag for a busy bride or a perfect bridesmaids gift.\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><a title=\"The Algonquin Leather Bag\" href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/shop/the-algonquin-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2141\"><img class=\"alignright\" alt=\"Cream and black leather drawstring handbag\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/BW-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\n<h2><b>The Algonquin</b> – our popular leather bag</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">This stylish handbag offers everyday functionality. Shown in cream and black leather. The size of this bag is perfect carry on a quick outing or move it from briefcase to tote and keep all your essentials in one place.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h2><b>The Sequoia</b><a title=\"The Sequoia Deerskin Bag\" href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/shop/the-sequoia/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2145\"><img class=\" wp-image-2145 alignright\" alt=\"sequoia-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/sequoia-bag2-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a> – our buttery soft deerskin bag</h2>\nThis buttery deerskin bucket bag is stylish and just the right size to hold all the essentials. Shown in brown and natural deerskin. You’ve got to feel it to appreciate how soft it is! You are sure to get many compliments when you carry this bag.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2><b>The Tahoe</b><a title=\"The Tahoe Vegan Bag\" href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/shop/the-tahoe/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2139\"><img class=\" wp-image-2139 alignright\" alt=\"tahoe-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/tahoe-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a> – a vegan bag</h2>\n<p align=\"left\">This casual and carefree bag is handy for any outing. Shown in denim and brocade, this bag is nature-friendly, since no animal products are used in its production.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h2><b>The Niagara</b><a title=\"The Niagara Bridal Bag\" href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/shop/the-niagara/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2142\"><img class=\" wp-image-2142 alignright\" alt=\"bridal-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/bridal-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a> – the essential bridal bag</h2>\n<p align=\"left\">This bag is perfect for a busy bride. It can hold lip gloss, small sprays, phone, money, feminine items and a handkerchief—all the things a bride needs on her big day. Shown in faux silk moiré fabric, adorned with beaded fringe and satin flowers. This is a perfect bridal shower gift.</p>\n<strong><em>These bags also make excellent gifts for your bridesmaids and wedding party. Ask us about special requests to match bridal gowns.</em></strong>','westcoast/east handbag styles','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-autosave','','','2013-04-21 19:21:42','2013-04-21 23:21:42','',2,'http://www.westcoast-east.com/2-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2252,2,'2013-04-21 12:04:26','2013-04-21 16:04:26','<h3></h3>\n[caption id=\"attachment_24\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"150\"]<a href=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/?attachment_id=24\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-24\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-24\" alt=\"Deerskin Essential Bag\" src=\"http://www.westcoast-east.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/purse-deerskin-accessor-150x150.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> The handbag that can fit all the necessaries and leave your hands free.[/caption]\n<h3>When will my handbag ship?</h3>\nItems in inventory will be shipped within 2 – 5 days of placing your order. Custom orders, such as our bridal bags, which we produce on a made-to-order basis, will ship within 1 – 3 weeks of the confirmation of your order.\n<h3>What is the westcoast/east policy for refunds, returns, and cancellation?</h3>\nUnused or defective items are eligible for a refund if returned within 30 days of delivery. Custom bags are not returnable, but we will try our best to make sure you have a satisfactory experience with our products.\n<h3>How are items shipped?</h3>\nItems are shipped UPS ground or via USPS priority mail, unless otherwise requested.\n<h3> How do I custom order a handbag?</h3>\nVisit our <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/contact/\">Contact Us</a> page and let us know what you are looking for.\n<h3> What is the westcoast/east privacy policy?</h3>\nYour privacy is important to us. To better protect your privacy the following notice explains the information we collect, how it is used, how it is safeguarded, and how to contact us if you have any concerns.\n<h3>Information collected</h3>\nAs part of the order process, the following information is collected from shoppers: Name, Shipping/Billing Address, E-mail Address, Phone Number, and Credit/Debit Card Information.\n<h4>How That Information Is Used</h4>\nThe information we collect is used to fill orders, to contact you if we have questions regarding your order, or to send occasional e-mails with special offers or notices of upcoming shows.\n<h3>Our Commitment To The Security of Your Data</h3>\nWe do not share your data with any partners or third parties. Your information is only used by us for the reasons outlined above.\n<h4>We also offer three options to secure your information:</h4>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(1) Shop Anonymously – West Coast / East does not store any of your information when you shop online. Whenever you shop at our online store, you will be asked to reenter information.\n(2) Remember Me – West Coast / East stores your billing information on a secure server and will be prefilled at checkout when you shop at our online store.\n(3) Express Checkout – All information, including billing and shipping address, credit card information, etc. is stored on a secure server and will be prefilled at checkout whenever you shop at our online store.</p>\n\n<h5>[box type=\"info\"]Please contact West Coast / East if you have a question that has not been addressed in our FAQ section above: <a href=\"mailto:contactus@westcoast-east.com\" target=\"_blank\">contactus@westcoast-east.com</a> [/box]</h5>','Frequently asked questions','','inherit','closed','closed','','2195-autosave','','','2013-04-21 12:04:26','2013-04-21 16:04:26','',2195,'http://www.westcoast-east.com/2195-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
